snippet.title: Diana and Roma feed the animals at the Emirates Park Zoo
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma feed the animals at the Emirates Park Zoo & Resort. This is a new hotel in Abu Dhabi, directly connected to the zoo. There are many beautiful natural monuments and animals around the resort. Diana and Roma came to this hotel for the weekend and had a great time!
Thanks for watching!
